snippet.title: BassTour gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for BassTour, Dos PC game produced by Olsen Outdoors in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/basstour/6193/
Exploring a lake and looking for fish in this old-school angling sim.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
